@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Governor's Highway Safety Program";
}

<style>
    .ghsp-page {
        color: #2d3748;
        padding-left: 4rem;
        padding-right: 4rem;
    }

        .ghsp-page .page-title {
            color: #497da8;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .ghsp-page .intro-text {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #4a5568;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .ghsp-page .section-label {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #2d3748;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .ghsp-page .reminder-panel {
            background-color: #edf1f7;
            border: 1px solid #cfd8e3;
            border-left: 4px solid #5a6e82;
            border-radius: 0.375rem;
            padding: 0.85rem 1.25rem;
        }

            .ghsp-page .reminder-panel ul {
                list-style: none;
                padding: 0;
                margin: 0;
            }

                .ghsp-page .reminder-panel ul li {
                    position: relative;
                    padding: 0.55rem 0 0.55rem 1.25rem;
                    color: #4a5568;
                    font-size: 1rem;
                    border-bottom: 1px solid #cfd8e3;
                    line-height: 1.4;
                }

                    .ghsp-page .reminder-panel ul li:last-child {
                        border-bottom: none;
                        padding-bottom: 0;
                    }

                    .ghsp-page .reminder-panel ul li::before {
                        content: '';
                        position: absolute;
                        left: 0;
                        top: 1rem;
                        width: 0.4rem;
                        height: 0.4rem;
                        background-color: #5a6e82;
                        border-radius: 50%;
                    }

                    .ghsp-page .reminder-panel ul li a {
                        color: #2b6cb0;
                        text-decoration: none;
                    }

                        .ghsp-page .reminder-panel ul li a:hover {
                            text-decoration: underline;
                        }

        .ghsp-page .content-block {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: #2d3748;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .ghsp-page .program-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 1.25rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .ghsp-page .program-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 0.25rem;
            border: 2px solid #000;
        }

        .ghsp-page .program-link {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            display: block;
        }

        .ghsp-page .program-card-header {
            background-color: #e7a81e;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 0.25rem;
            padding: 0.85rem 0.75rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
            transition: filter 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
        }

        .ghsp-page .program-link:hover .program-card-header,
        .ghsp-page .program-link:focus-visible .program-card-header {
            filter: brightness(1.08);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(231, 168, 30, 0.35);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

    @@media (max-width: 991.98px) {
        .ghsp-page .page-title {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
        }

        .ghsp-page .program-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }

    @@media (max-width: 575.98px) {
        .ghsp-page .program-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>

<div class="ghsp-page py-4">

    <h1 class="page-title">Governor's Highway Safety Program (GHSP)</h1>

    <p class="intro-text mb-4">
        The Governor's Highway Safety Program (GHSP) is the lead agency for West Virginia's participation
        in federally mandated and funded behavioral highway safety improvement measures. The mission of the
        WV GHSP is to reduce crashes, injuries, and fatalities on West Virginia's roadways by encouraging,
        promoting, and supporting highway safety throughout the state.
    </p>

    <!-- Program Tiles -->
    <p class="section-label mt-4">Programs &amp; Focus Areas</p>
    <div class="program-grid">
        <div class="program-card">
            <a class="program-link" href="https://transportation.wv.gov/dmv/safety/cps/Pages/default.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                <div class="program-card-header">Child Passenger Safety</div>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="program-card">
            <a class="program-link" href="https://transportation.wv.gov/DMV/Safety/Pages/Distracted-Driving.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                <div class="program-card-header">Distracted Driving</div>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="program-card">
            <a class="program-link" href="https://transportation.wv.gov/DMV/Safety/Pages/Impaired-Driving.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                <div class="program-card-header">Impaired Driving</div>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="program-card">
            <a class="program-link" href="https://transportation.wv.gov/DMV/Safety/MSP/Pages/default.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                <div class="program-card-header">Motorcycle Safety</div>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="program-card">
            <a class="program-link" href="https://transportation.wv.gov/DMV/Safety/Pages/Occupant-Protection.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                <div class="program-card-header">Occupant Protection</div>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="program-card">
            <a class="program-link" href="https://transportation.wv.gov/DMV/Safety/Pages/Speed-Enforcement.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                <div class="program-card-header">Speed Enforcement</div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Regional Programs -->
    <p class="section-label">Regional Programs</p>
    <p class="content-block">
        The state is divided into regional traffic safety programs that cover all fifty-five counties.
        Each region has a designated regional coordinator to develop and implement the counter-measures
        that their regions require to lower the total crashes, injuries, and fatalities on the roadways
        in West Virginia.
    </p>

    <!-- About the Programs -->
    <p class="section-label">About the Programs</p>
    <p class="content-block">
        The GHSP, along with our highway safety partners and advocates, works to prevent crashes, fatalities,
        and injuries and make West Virginia roads safer by focusing on Occupant Protection, Child Passenger
        Safety, Impaired Driving prevention, Distracted Driving prevention, and Speed Enforcement.
    </p>
    <p class="content-block">
        The Motorcycle Safety Program (MSP) promotes awareness of motorcycle safety practices and laws and
        encourages riders to obtain their Class F Endorsement. The ATV Safety and Awareness Program fosters
        all-terrain vehicle safety, as well as awareness of West Virginia's laws governing proper and safe
        use of ATVs. Target Red is a campaign that regional traffic safety programs use to spread awareness
        of the dangers of red light and stop sign violations.
    </p>

