        <ul>
            <li><a href="https://transportation.wv.gov/DMV/Safety/Pages/GHSP-R-D-M.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GHSP Reports, Data, and Manuals</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://transportation.wv.gov/DMV/Safety/Pages/Law-Enforcement-Officers.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Law Enforcement Officer Training</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://transportation.wv.gov/DMV/Safety/Regions/Pages/default.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Highway Safety Program Regions</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://transportation.wv.gov/DMV/Safety/Pages/Highway-Safety-Staff-Directory.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Highway Safety Staff Directory</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://transportation.wv.gov/DMV/Safety/Pages/Uniform-Traffic-Citations.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Uniform Traffic Citations</a></li>
