    <p class="section-label">Highway Safety-Related Links</p>
    <div class="reminder-panel">
        <ul>
            <li><a href="http://ghsa.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Governor's Highway Safety Association</a></li>
            <li><a href="http://www.nhtsa.dot.gov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">National Highway Traffic Safety Administration</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://cdan.dot.gov/STSI/stsi.htm#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Traffic Safety Info — Quick, easy access to data</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://das.wv.gov/JCS/law-enforcement/Pages/default.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">West Virginia Law Enforcement Professional Standards (LEPS) Training</a></li>
            <li><a href="http://www.wvsp.gov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">West Virginia State Police</a></li>
